    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/4b19440be46ac0cf55218081f59a82f7.poster.avif?t=1758053618\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/4b19440be46ac0cf55218081f59a82f7.webm?t=1758053618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/4b19440be46ac0cf55218081f59a82f7.mp4?t=1758053618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Frame of Mind - A game of thoughts》是一款简短而温馨的叙事游戏，让你通过不同人生阶段的回忆和物品，探索角色的内心世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款内省式游戏，旨在分享包括开发者在内的一群神经多样性酷儿在成长过程中经历的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/368318ea74097e71e3b1f000f3017014.poster.avif?t=1758053618\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/368318ea74097e71e3b1f000f3017014.webm?t=1758053618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/368318ea74097e71e3b1f000f3017014.mp4?t=1758053618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演角色，在搬出去后回到自己的童年故居。你会找到哪些纪念物？会回忆起什么样的思绪？他们能感到幸福吗？也许不能。你可以选择保留或丢弃哪些想法，帮助他们找到更好的心境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/c6b78ef1f2e0035d81e127021efffb64.poster.avif?t=1758053618\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/c6b78ef1f2e0035d81e127021efffb64.webm?t=1758053618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235110/extras/c6b78ef1f2e0035d81e127021efffb64.mp4?t=1758053618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然游戏尽可能友善和易于体验，但它也展现了社会对“与众不同”的孩子施加的压力。如果你想寻求纯粹的逃避现实体验，这款游戏可能不太适合你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有时会显得沉重，但它的核心是共情，并希望能分享真实的感受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏和手册中提供了详细的内容提示（请查看右下角的链接列表）。</p>",
